TextEng: Tell me what is happening here.
Text: 여기서 무슨 일이 벌어지고 있는지 말해.

TextEng: What going on here?
Explain yourself! I don't trust anyone here!
Text: 설명해! 여기선 아무도 믿을 수 없어!

TextEng: Me not trust you! Tell me what go on here!
Text: 나 너 안 믿어! 무슨 일인지 말해!

TextEng: I'm not here about you. I have no interest.
Text: 네 일 때문에 온 게 아냐. 관심 없어.

TextEng: Me not here for your problems. Me not care.
Text: 나 네 문제 때문에 온 거 아냐. 관심 없어.

TextEng: I said I have no interest!
Me say me not care!
Tell me what you need?
What you need?
I need information! This is all so confusing!
Me wants informations! This too confusing!
I am losing interest. Hurry the hell up.
Me lose patience. Hurry up soon!
So I search blindly for something you won't talk about?
Text: 그러니까 네가 말해주지 않는 걸 눈 먼 채로 찾으라고?

TextEng: Me wander blind looking for stuff you don't talk about?
Text: 나 보고 네가 안 말하는 거 찾아 헤매라고?

TextEng: I'll go look around, then.
Me go look around, then.
This is ridiculous. I have no interest in your ramblings!
Text: 이건 말도 안 돼. 횡설수설에 관심 없어!

TextEng: Me gots no interest in your blabber!
I have a journal that says some nasty things.
Me gots book that says bad things.
I already have a scepter from one of your siblings.
Text: 이미 네 형제 중 하나에게서 홀을 얻었어.

TextEng: Me gots scepter from somebody of your family.
I found this strange phylactery?
Me gots phylacter-whasis jam jar thing.
Text: 이 뭐시기... 항아리 같은 거 있어.

TextEng: I have a scepter from your siblings.
Me gots scepter thing from famliy of yours.
I have this strange phylactery?
Me gots phylacter-thing jar?
Could you repeat what you said before?
Text: 전에 한 말 다시 해줄 수 있어?

TextEng: You go over what you said before?
I have a journal that says very damning things.
Text: 아주 치명적인 내용이 담긴 일지가 있어.

TextEng: Me gots book that says bad things.
Goodbye.
<StartAction>Show him Nari's scepter.</Start>
<StartAction>Show him Jardak's scepter.</Start>
Nevermind.
<StartAction>Show him the scepters from Nari and Jardak.</Start>
I need more information.
Me needs more information.
I will trust you. What do you need done?
Me trust. What you need done?
I don't care.
Me not care.
Those poor villagers! You were a part of this?
Text: 그 불쌍한 마을 사람들! 네가 거기에 가담했다고?

TextEng: Those poor villager guys! You jerks!
Text: 불쌍한 마을 사람들! 이 나쁜 놈들!

TextEng: So you trapped him? How long ago was that?
You finally trapped him then? When was that?
Enough of your blather! What now?
Enough of this stuff! What now?
So what needs to be done?
What needs to be done?
Everyone is dead? Your family? The village?
Everybody dead? Your family? The village?
The villagers sold their own? They let them be killed?
Text: 마을 사람들이 자기들끼리 팔아먹었다고? 죽게 내버려뒀고?

TextEng: Villagers gave up their own for payments?
Text: 마을 사람들이 돈 받고 이웃을 팔았어?

TextEng: You've been here for how long?
You here for how long?
<StartAction>Show him the scepters from Nari and Jardak.</Start>
Goodbye.
How do I put an end to this?
How me end this?
I should destroy everything! Including you! Nobody is innocent!
Text: 전부 파괴해야겠어! 너 포함해서! 무고한 자는 없어!

TextEng: Me stop everything! Even you! All bad!
Text: 전부 없애버릴 거야! 너도! 다 나빠!

TextEng: I'll put an end to all of this.
Me stop all of this.
I still think I should kill you too.
Text: 아직 너도 죽여야 할 것 같은데.

TextEng: Me still think you die too.
Text: 나 아직도 너 죽여야 할 것 같아.

TextEng: What happens if Karlat's destroyed? His spell caused this.
Text: 칼랏이 파괴되면 어떻게 되지? 그의 주문이 이걸 일으켰잖아.

TextEng: What happens if Karlat destroyed? His spell make all this.
Text: 칼랏 파괴되면 어떻게 돼? 걔 주문이 이거 만들었잖아.
